Description: Dataset from Visser et al. 2015 published in Psychoneuroendocrinology. Please refer to the publication for details regarding the participants and experiment.

Please cite the following references if you use these data:
Visser, R M, A E Kunze, B Westhoff, H S Scholte, and M Kindt. 2015. “Representational Similarity Analysis Offers a Preview of the Noradrenergic Modulation of Long-Term Fear Memory at the Time of Encoding.” Psychoneuroendocrinology 55: 8–20. http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.psyneuen.2015.01.021

Release history:
9 February 2021 - initial release
